{"type": "article", "id": 25648, "title": "\"反应系列\"家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-19T07:13:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607132043clmS8VpIKCgbsFdh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本设计师北川大辅在米兰设计周上推出的\"反应系列\"。他展出了 5 组常见的家具，在看似普通的外形中拥有细微的设计感。比如月亮灯是让灯光反射到墙面上，从正面看像是月食现象。正方形的独立沙发只有两边有靠背，围成了一个三角形的空间，给人蜷缩的安全感。花瓶则刻意做出了一排凹槽，可以让插在上面的画更整齐。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132040erptYZHnmOJGV19T.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132041hKHz8GvqQANLpjcX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132041UKDekR2HoBVYr9Ph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132042bKCAjUWe45Z7w2J9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132042X5yNh0OoHz8pC6Qw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071320427FoZz2H0imUW8kVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}